race.comment: ATTRITION (1) resumes. 1400m is short of his best and he gives away weight but he is the class of this field. Can settle close to the speed from the low gate and the Terang jump-out will have forward enough. Can make a bold return. CAFE MILLENIUM (4) resumes from a short break. No doubt he will head straight back from the wide draw but if the pace is genuine he will take some holding out. REGAL ZEUS (3) bounced straight back to form at the latest when leading pillar-to-post in the LR Lord Stakes. Drops back in trip with a month between runs and is drawn to advantage. Sure to take reeling in. JUSTADEEL (11) returns and is a noted fresh performer. Gets in low at the weights and loves this trip. A lot to like.
